OL,3,CDurrell name new chair following
OL,4,CMatthew Hatchwell's resignation
OL,6,FNiall Husbands has been named as the
OL,7,Fnew Chair of the Durrell Wildlife
OL,8,FConservation Trust following Matthew
OL,9,FHatchwell's resignation.
OL,11,FThe charity's Board of Trustees voted
OL,12,Fhim in unanimously and he will start
OL,13,Fimmediately while Matthew will
OL,14,Fcontinue as a Trustee.
OL,16,FSpeaking about the appointment, Niall
OL,17,Fsaid: "It truly is an incredible
OL,18,Fhonour to be elected as the new Chair
OL,19,Fat Durrell.
