OL,4,CMatthew Hatchwell's resignation
OL,6,FMatthew will now focus his time on
OL,7,Fconservation consultancy work after
OL,8,Fserving as Chair since October 2023.
OL,10,FHe was in charge when more than 100
OL,11,Fmembers of the Trust called for the
OL,12,FBoard to be ousted last March,
OL,13,Ffollowing allegations about the poor
OL,14,Ftreatment of animals and staff
OL,15,Fbullying, as well as concerns over the
OL,16,Fdirection the charity was heading.
