OL,6,FThey comprehensively survived a
OL,7,Fhistoric vote of no confidence but a
OL,8,Fnew Board of Trustees - including
OL,9,FMatthew - was elected by members in
OL,10,FDecember.
OL,12,FFollowing his resignation, he said:
OL,13,F"None of us knew when I took on the
OL,14,Frole as Chair what the next 18 months
OL,15,Fwould hold.
OL,17,F"Although it was a very challenging
OL,18,Ftime in many respects, it was also
OL,19,Fimmensely rewarding and a great
OL,20,Fprivilege to lead the Board through
OL,21,Fthat period.
